Andover Group, a Virginia generalpartnership, said it mailed proxies soliciting votes for aslate of nominees to HBO and Co's board of directors.   Last week, HBO and Co sent a letter urging shareholdersagainst the proxies.    Andover said HBO has consistently refused to provide itwith internal financial information it considers essential toformulate an acquisition offer. If its nominees are elected,Andover said it will make a proposal to buy HBO on terms andconditions to be determined at that time.    The annual meeting is scheduled for April 30. Reuter&#3;